<span id="freeTextContainer8292858371110161926">I am bored of books that turn to scriptures to make meaning of current human existence. I wish someone would give an entirely new perspective , something fresh , the way children look at things with new eyes and new meanings, children whose minds have not yet been conditioned by the ways of the world (and books!) Very bored with the prescriptive life stages, vanaprasthashrama and it’s dull melancholy reflected in the book does not make it exciting enough for me to continue...</span>

          </span>
